ellite Awards]]\n| [[22nd Satellite Awards|10 February 2018]]\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Film|Best Film]]\n| ''God's Own Country''\n| {{won|Tied win}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{efn|Tied with ''[[Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri]]''}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/dunkirk-the-shape-of-water-lead-satellite-award-nominations/|title='''Dunkirk'', ''The Shape of Water'' Lead Satellite Award Nominations|work=[[TheWrap]]|date=28 November 2017|accessdate=28 November 2017|first=Steve|last=Pond}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\"| [[Stockholm International Film Festival]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 20 November 2017\n| Best Direction \n| {{sort|Lee|Francis Lee}}\n| {{won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"3\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stockholmfilmfestival.se/en/news/2017/award-winners-stockholm-28th-international-film-festival|title=Award Winners at the Stockholm 28th International Film Festival|publisher=[[Stockholm International Film Festival]]|date=20 November 2017|accessdate=20 November 2017|archiveurl=https://archive.is/aINX6|archivedate=21 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Male Actor\n| {{sort|O'Connor|[[Josh O'Connor]]}}\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Bronze Horse\n| ''God's Own Country''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| [[Sundance Film Festival]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[2017 Sundance Film Festival|28 January 2017]]\n| World Cinema Directing Award\n| {{sort|Lee|Francis Lee}}\n| {{won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sundance.org/pdf/press-releases/2016-11-30-2017-sundance-film-festival-competition-and-next-final6.pdf|title=2017 Sundance Film Festival: Competition And Next Lineup Announced|type=Press release|date=29 November 2016|accessdate=21 November 2017|publisher=[[Sundance Film Festival]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171121135054/http://www.sundance.org/pdf/press-releases/2016-11-30-2017-sundance-film-festival-competition-and-next-final6.pdf|archivedate=21 November 2017