n:center;\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tiff.ro/en/stiri/winners-transilvania-iff-2017|title=The Winners of Transilvania IFF 2017!|publisher=[[Transilvania International Film Festival]]|accessdate=17 October 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725005641/http://tiff.ro/en/stiri/winners-transilvania-iff-2017|archivedate=25 July 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| Transilvania Trophy\n| ''God's Own Country''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Writers' Guild of Great Britain|Writers' Guild of Great Britain Awards]]\n| 15 January 2018\n| Best First Screenplay\n| Francis Lee\n| {{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://writersguild.org.uk/writers-guild-awards-shortlist-2018/|title=Writers' Guild Awards Shortlist 2018|publisher=[[Writers' Guild of Great Britain]]|date=5 December 2017|accessdate=5 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Zagreb Film Festival]]\n| 18 November 2017\n| The Golden Pram\n| ''God's Own Country''\n| {{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zff.hr/en/predstavljen-program-15-zff-a/|title=15th ZFF Presents Program!|publisher=[[Zagreb Film Festival]]|date=2 November 2017|accessdate=2 November 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171121144211/http://zff.hr/en/predstavljen-program-15-zff-a/|archivedate=21 November 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Notes===\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|5635086|God's Own Country}}\n* {{Mojo title|godsowncountry|God's Own Country}}\n* {{Rotten Tomatoes|gods_own_country_2017|God's Own Country}}\n* {{Metacritic film|gods-own-country|God's Own Country}}\n*[https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/apr/28/countryside-the-levelling-gods-own-country-abandon-inner-city ''Guardian'' article from April 2017 about the film and fellow \"countryside movie\" ''The Levelling'']\n\n{{BIFA BestBritishFilm}}\n{{Empire Award for Best British Film}}\n{{Satellite Award Best Motion Picture}}\n\n{{DEFA